As of the [[2020 United States census]], there were 846 people, 322 households, and 212 families residing in the city.<ref>{{Cite web|title=S1101 HOUSEHOLDS AND FAMILIES - 2020: Center Hill city, Florida|url=https://data.census.gov/table?q=Center+Hill+city;+Florida+&tid=ACSST5Y2020.S1101|website=[[United States Census Bureau]]}}</ref>

